Class GraphData

  • java.lang.Object
    • GraphData

  • public class GraphData
extends java.lang.Object
    Class containing the GRAPH ADT Use this alongside 'edges' and 'nodes' classes Can represent basic graphs up to 20 nodes and edges Can traverse basic graphs
